      "id": "task_1756933946746_egbh0ooez",
      "title": "Create comprehensive template library system with business automation categories",
      "description": "Implement a comprehensive template library system to compete with n8n, including categorized templates for:\n\n**TEMPLATE CATEGORIES:**\n1. **Business Automation**: CRM workflows, marketing campaigns, sales pipelines, lead management\n2. **Data Processing & ETL**: Data transformation pipelines, database synchronization, API data collection\n3. **DevOps & CI/CD**: Deployment automation, testing workflows, monitoring and alerting\n4. **Social Media Management**: Content publishing, engagement tracking, cross-platform posting\n5. **E-commerce Automation**: Order processing, inventory management, customer service workflows\n6. **Financial & Accounting**: Invoice processing, payment automation, financial reporting\n\n**TECHNICAL IMPLEMENTATION:**\n1. **Database Schema**: Extend schema with template categories, tags, usage tracking, ratings\n2. **Template Storage**: JSONB workflow templates with metadata, version control, usage analytics\n3. **Discovery System**: Search, filtering, recommendations based on user behavior and industry\n4. **Template Management**: Creation, editing, publishing, versioning, and quality control\n5. **Integration Points**: Seamless template instantiation in workflow editor\n\n**SUCCESS CRITERIA:**\n- 50+ high-quality templates across all categories\n- Template discovery and search functionality\n- One-click template instantiation\n- Template usage analytics and optimization\n- Community rating and review system\n- Template versioning and updates",
