      "title": "Complete test infrastructure migration for remaining API test files",
      "description": "Complete the migration of remaining 118+ API test files to use the new bun/vitest compatible test infrastructure. The migration patterns have been proven successful (improving test pass rates from 15% to 89%) and need to be applied across all API test files.\n\nAFFECTED FILES:\n- All files in apps/sim/app/api/**/*.test.ts\n- Approximately 60+ API route test files\n- Focus on high-priority workflow, authentication, and core API tests\n\nMIGRATION APPROACH:\n1. Apply working patterns from successful migrations (versions, collaboration)\n2. Replace vi.doMock() with module-level vi.mock() patterns\n3. Use enhanced test utilities from apps/sim/app/api/__test-utils__/\n4. Implement proper authentication and database mocking\n5. Add comprehensive logging and production-ready comments\n\nSUCCESS CRITERIA:\n- 90%+ test pass rate across all migrated files\n- All authentication tests returning proper status codes (200/201 not 403/500)\n- Production-ready test patterns with comprehensive logging\n- Full compatibility with bun/vitest environment",
